            "title": "即月期指開跌107點  低水91點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報25798，跌107點或0.41%，低水91點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科指期貨開報5991，跌30點或5%，低水13點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國指期貨開報9221，跌43點或0.46%，低水38點。</p>\n</div>",
