            "title": "正力新能折讓7.89%配股",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">正力新能(03677)配股集資，配售價每股H股10.98元，較上日收市價11.92港元折價約7.89%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"正力新能招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/03677.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"正力新能招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/03677.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">正力新能招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">配售股份約經配發及發行配售股份擴大後的已發行H股的3.09%，及已發行股份總數的1.80%，集資5.04億元。</p>\n</div>",
