        {
            "title": "歐股收升　法股升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">歐洲股市上升，法國股市升至7個月高位，法國政府避過國會兩項不信任動議。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"歐股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250318_FI_source-ap_Britain_Financial_Markets-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">歐股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">泛歐指數Stoxx 600收市反彈0.69%，報571點，為全日最高位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國富時100指數收報9436點，升11點，升幅0.12%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">法國CAC指數收報8188點，升111點，升幅1.38%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">德國DAX指數收報24272點，升90點，升幅0.38%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">意大利富時MIB指數收報42374點，上行1.12%或467點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">西班牙IBEX 35指數收報15645點，上升0.48%或75點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">雀巢股價大升逾9%，創自2008年以來最大單日升幅，公司的銷售額好於預期，並宣布裁員1.6萬人。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15349097-%e6%ad%90%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%87%e3%80%80%e6%b3%95%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1%e3%80%80",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250306_FI_source-web_eu-stock-1-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-17 08:40:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "海西新藥暗盤中段較招股價上限高逾29%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">海西新藥(02637)明天掛牌，該股暗盤大幅高開，中段明顯回順，截至下午約5時15分暗盤價約112元，較招股範圍上限86.4元高逾29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">輝立證券交易平台顯示，該股暗盤以172元開市，較招股範圍上限高接近1倍，最低曾105元，仍高於招股範圍上限逾21%。</p>\n</div>",
